³avenue of media transfer and the exchange of data, photos   ³
³and documents have begun.  We are also in the process of    ³
³establishing communication links with the European UFO      ³
³Bulletin Board System.                                      ³
³                                                            ³
³All data, photographs, newsletters, catalogues and          ³
³newsclippings will be available to MUFON Members and the    ³
